# NOT *.npy: server/cloud_mcp/data/docs_index/embeddings.npy is the built
# docs-index vector file and must be committed as package data (matching
# every other machine repo in the family) — a blanket *.npy rule here
# previously ignored it silently, so a real embeddings.npy could be
# generated and would never actually get committed.
# uv tool run resolves its own dependencies; a committed lock file would drift without benefit
server/uv.lock
